data.description: Welcome to this stunning waterfront 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located on the picturesque shores of Lake Tyler East. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room adorned with a floor-to-ceiling brick wood-burning fireplace creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The large windows offer breathtaking views of the tranquil lake allowing natural light to flood the room. The open concept design ensures seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it perfect for entertaining guests. The kitchen is a chef's dream boasting stainless steel appliances, elegant granite countertops, a convenient breakfast bar, and a separate formal dining room for more intimate gatherings. Adjacent to the living room you'll find a spacious office space providing a quiet and productive environment to work from home or pursue your hobbies. The master suite is a luxurious retreat featuring vaulted ceilings that add a touch of grandeur. The suite includes a generous walk-in closet, double vanity sinks in the bathroom, and a relaxing jetted soaking tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Outdoor living is a delight in this property. The covered back patio is an ideal spot for hosting family get-togethers or simply enjoying a peaceful afternoon while overlooking the shimmering lake. The fenced yard offers a safe space for your children and pets to run freely and play. For those who love water activities, the boat house is a highlight. It features two lifts to accommodate your watercraft, a storage room for all your equipment, and a spacious deck where you can sit back, relax, and soak in the beauty of the water. Don't miss this opportunity to own a waterfront oasis on Lake Tyler East. With its stunning features, convenient amenities, and breathtaking views, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort, luxury, and natural beauty.
